  "content": "<div class=\"content-main relative\">\n <h1 class=\"block text-[4rem] text-[var(--dark)] leading-[4.4rem] font-semibold mb-[5px]\">Canada sẵn s&agrave;ng nối lại đ&agrave;m ph&aacute;n thương mại với Mỹ sau đoạn video g&acirc;y tranh c&atilde;i</h1>\n <div class=\"content-meta flex items-center flex-wrap flex-row text-[1.3rem] leading-[2rem] font-normal text-[#999] truncate h-[30px] mb-[10px] [&amp;&gt;:not(:first-child)]:ml-[25px]\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n   <a href=\"/bao-nhan-dan-nhan-dan-p14.epi\" class=\"bm-card-source flex items-center shrink-0\" title=\"B&aacute;o Nh&acirc;n D&acirc;n\">\n    <figure class=\"image opacity-80 w-auto h-[16px]\" style=\"width:58.75px;height:20px\" aria-label=\"Logo nh&agrave; xuất bản\">\n     <picture>\n      <source srcset=\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/4e023e6de32e0a70533f.png\" type=\"image/avif\"></source>\n      <source srcset=\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/4e023e6de32e0a70533f.png\" type=\"image/webp\"></source>\n      <img src=\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/4e023e6de32e0a70533f.png\" alt=\"B&aacute;o Nh&acirc;n D&acirc;n\" width=\"188\" height=\"64\" />\n     </picture>\n    </figure></a>\n   <span><button class=\"relative text-[14px] leading-[normal] font-normal text-center cursor-pointer normal-case border-0 transition-button disabled:shadow-none disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed follow-button flex items-center item-star ml-[10px]\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" title=\"Theo d&otilde;i &quot;Nh&acirc;n D&acirc;n&quot;\" aria-label=\"Button\"><i class=\"icon inline-block font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-star text-[var(--primary)]\"></i></button></span>\n  </div>\n  <time datetime=\"2025-10-25T07:30:00.000Z\">25/10/2025</time>\n  <a href=\"/mark-carney-t38898371.epi\" class=\"related inline !text-[#adb5bd] hover:!text-[var(--primary)]\">420\n   <!-- --> li&ecirc;n quan</a>\n  <a href=\"/canada-san-sang-noi-lai-dam-phan-thuong-mai-voi-my-sau-doan-video-gay-tranh-cai-r53582180.epi\" class=\"origin item-origin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><i class=\"icon inline-block font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-copy text-[13px] mr-[5px]\"></i><span>Gốc</span></a>\n  <i class=\"bm-icon inline-block bg-[url(https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/bm-icon-2.0.3.png)] bg-[length:100px_4250px] align-middle bg-[0_-773px] w-[23px] h-[23px]\"></i>\n </div>\n <h3 class=\"sapo block text-[2rem] leading-[2.6rem] font-semibold text-[var(--dark)] p-[10px] bg-[#f2f4f5]\">Ng&agrave;y 24/10, Thủ tướng Canada Mark Carney tuy&ecirc;n bố Ottawa sẵn s&agrave;ng nối lại c&aacute;c cuộc đ&agrave;m ph&aacute;n thương mại với Mỹ, sau khi Tổng thống Donald Trump tạm dừng hoạt động n&agrave;y v&igrave; một đoạn video phản đối thuế nhập khẩu do ch&iacute;nh quyền bang Ontario c&ocirc;ng bố.</h3>\n <div class=\"content-body text-[2rem] leading-[2.6rem] text-black mt-[15px] break-words overflow-hidden [&amp;_h1]:mb-[15px] [&amp;_h2]:mb-[15px] [&amp;_h3]:mb-[15px] [&amp;_h4]:mb-[15px] [&amp;_h5]:mb-[15px] [&amp;_p]:mb-[15px] [&amp;&gt;div]:mb-[15px]\">\n  <div class=\"video-wrapper max-h-[80vh]\" style=\"width:625px;height:351.461038961039px;background:url(https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/player-default-03.png) no-repeat center center;background-size:cover\"></div>\n  <p class=\"text\">Thủ tướng <a class=\"tag-link\" href=\"/canada-tag3746.epi\">Canada</a> Mark Carney tuy&ecirc;n bố sẵn s&agrave;ng nối lại đ&agrave;m ph&aacute;n thương mại với Mỹ sau khi &ocirc;ng Trump tạm dừng.</p>\n  <p class=\"text\">Bang Ontario d&ugrave;ng h&igrave;nh ảnh cắt gh&eacute;p, chỉnh sửa của Cố Tổng thống <a class=\"tag-link\" href=\"/my-tag81.epi\">Mỹ</a> Ronald Reagan để ngầm chỉ tr&iacute;ch Nh&agrave; Trắng.</p>\n  <p class=\"text\">Bang Ontario sẽ tạm dừng ph&aacute;t s&oacute;ng đoạn video từ ng&agrave;y 28/10 để giảm căng thẳng.</p>\n  <p class=\"text\">&Ocirc;ng Carney khẳng định Canada vẫn cam kết hợp t&aacute;c với Mỹ v&agrave; hướng tới xem x&eacute;t lại Hiệp định USMCA trong năm tới.</p>\n  <p class=\"text body-author text-right\"><strong>B&Ugrave;I ĐỨC</strong></p>\n </div>\n <div class=\"pswp\" tabindex=\"-1\" role=\"dialog\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n  <div class=\"pswp__bg\"></div>\n  <div class=\"pswp__scroll-wrap\">\n   <div class=\"pswp__container\">\n    <div class=\"pswp__item\"></div>\n    <div class=\"pswp__item\"></div>\n    <div class=\"pswp__item\"></div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"pswp__ui pswp__ui--hidden\">\n    <div class=\"pswp__top-bar\">\n     <div class=\"pswp__counter\"></div>\n     <button type=\"button\" class=\"pswp__button pswp__button--close\" title=\"Close (Esc)\"></button>\n     <button type=\"button\" class=\"pswp__button pswp__button--share\" title=\"Share\"></button>\n     <button type=\"button\" class=\"pswp__button pswp__button--fs\" title=\"Toggle fullscreen\"></button>\n     <button type=\"button\" class=\"pswp__button pswp__button--zoom\" title=\"Zoom in/out\"></button>\n     <div class=\"pswp__preloader\">\n      <div class=\"pswp__preloader__icn\">\n       <div class=\"pswp__preloader__cut\">\n        <div class=\"pswp__preloader__donut\"></div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"pswp__share-modal pswp__share-modal--hidden pswp__single-tap\">\n     <div class=\"pswp__share-tooltip\"></div>\n    </div>\n    <button type=\"button\" class=\"pswp__button pswp__button--arrow--left\" title=\"Previous (arrow left)\"></button>\n    <button type=\"button\" class=\"pswp__button pswp__button--arrow--right\" title=\"Next (arrow right)\"></button>\n    <div class=\"pswp__caption\">\n     <div class=\"pswp__caption__center\"></div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"content-social absolute top-[55px] w-[40px] h-full ml-[-75px]\">\n  <div class=\"content-social-cont